"AI Overview

Grounded DI LLC is an AI and technology company pioneering Deterministic Intelligence (DI). They focus on transforming passive, probabilistic Large Language Models (LLMs) into auditable, rule-constrained logic systems designed to prevent hallucinations and eliminate hidden logic drift. 

Key Areas of Focus

Deterministic Execution: The firm is building an AI infrastructure layer designed to ensure auditable, replayable AI execution, which is particularly vital in highly regulated fields like legal, auditing, and healthcare.

Rule-Constrained Logic: Their DI model prioritizes strict adherence to constraints and metrics so that a specific input consistently yields a predictable, reproducible output.

Intellectual Property: They have actively filed for trademarks related to Deterministic Artificial Intelligence with the USPTO."

